A,B
F_p
A + B = \left\{ {\left. {a + b} \right|a \in A,b \in B} \right\}
\min \left( {p,\left| A \right| + \left| B \right| - 1} \right) \le \left| {A + B} \right|
\left| A \right| \cdot \left| B \right|
m=|A|
n=|B|
p
x\in G=\Bbb{Z}_p
x
P_2(m,n,p)\ge P_1(m,n,p).
x
 \begin{aligned} \left(1-\frac1p\right)^{mn}&=\prod_{j=0}^{n-1}\left(1-\frac1p\right)^m\\ &>\prod_{j=0}^{n-1}\left(1-\frac1{p-j}\right)^m\\ &>\prod_{j=0}^{n-1}\left(1-\frac{m}{p-j}\right)= \prod_{j=0}^{n-1}\left(\frac{p-m-j}{p-j}\right). \end{aligned} 
